description:
This is a 29 minute workout called 'Pilates Reformer Workout | 30 min | Full Body' from the channel Dez Fit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: This quick, but intense Pilates reformer workout will give you a full body burn in just 30 min. Perfect for when you're short on time. (extra emphasis on upper body and shoulders)
Hope you enjoy!
